# Production build. tsc/lint/vitest never exercise `vite build`, so a
# broken production build (vite-plugin closeBundle crashes, unresolved
# `?raw`/asset imports, plugin/dep regressions) is otherwise invisible
# until deploy — exactly how two such bugs sat undetected on main.
# `tsc` above already covers the `tsc &&` half of `npm run build`, so
# run `vite build` directly (leaner, no double typecheck). Assumes
# `npm run build:wasm` has populated src/assets/puzzles/ (the same
# precondition `npm run build` already documents).
npx vite build
